{"tid":1467494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非同我入黎","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:01.000Z","uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f8d141cff72ab2c0c4370a8a261b8454865a74","tid":1467494,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"聽日一定有大批藍絲或想割既和理非非追問機場事件，<br />\n<br />\n我決定清一色學班黑警答「可能唔完美，但可接受，需要改善、改進。」<br />\n<br />\n講好玩核彈都唔割，唔係阻下人上機，圍個死人公安同環時就割啊？<br />\n唔好再同我講鬼，前線打人我都撐，我嫌打得個環時記者少添！成日作新聞！"},{"pid":"5d0c3637d1e0d341a7083af4067124c3ebd282f0","tid":1467494,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:54.000Z","msg":"自推十野"},{"pid":"3c809219f2a376f76fb4dfab02923c8cdd8e643c","tid":1467494,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"21adca7a5e31049157171707393b64516854f24d","tid":1467494,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"69210cef0bf21940dada63571d11e369ce6a483c","tid":1467494,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"70712a23b36563c61b8859231f323a608e570bd3","tid":1467494,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f7ec0d94c5d2a10a31040700f75df33d3010f3e8","tid":1467494,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a0118235f01087fd6582abd2e66441254084c5e7","tid":1467494,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"94ef76cdd17103e6d1cd5ec805b9979b1fd32971","tid":1467494,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"bc8ead1973aaaeed1122df8bd7c099faa6270115","tid":1467494,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0